            <td style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">No (se programan y listo)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Sí (lightjockey en vivo)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Gobos (patrones)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">No</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; text-align:center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Sí (spot y beam)</td>
          </tr>
